'''树莓派'''（{{lang-en|'''Raspberry Pi'''}}）[[英國|英國]][[树莓派基金会|树莓派基金会]]开发的微型单板计算机，目的是以低價[[硬體|硬體]]及[[自由軟體|自由軟體]]促进学校的基本[[电脑科学|电脑科学]]教育。<ref name=cheatsheet>{{cite web |url=http://www.silicon.com/technology/hardware/2011/10/03/raspberry-pi-cheat-sheet-39748024/ |title=Raspberry Pi: Cheat Sheet |publisher=Silicon.com |accessdate=2012-05-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106180235/http://www.silicon.com/technology/hardware/2011/10/03/raspberry-pi-cheat-sheet-39748024/ |archivedate=2012-01-06 }}</ref><ref name="faq">{{cite web | title = FAQs | publisher = Raspberry Pi Foundation | url = http://www.raspberrypi.org/?page_id=8 | accessdate = 2011-10-06 | archive-date = 2011-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111101045949/http://www.raspberrypi.org/?page_id=8 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Cellan-Jones | first = Rory | authorlink = Rory Cellan-Jones | title = A £15 computer to inspire young programmers | publisher = BBC News | date = 2011-05-05 | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/thereporters/rorycellanjones/2011/05/a_15_computer_to_inspire_young.html | access-date = 2012-11-23 | archive-date = 2011-05-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110507072250/http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/thereporters/rorycellanjones/2011/05/a_15_computer_to_inspire_young.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | last = Price | first = Peter | title = Can a £15 computer solve the programming gap? | publisher = [[Click_(TV_programme)|BBC Click]] | date = 2011-06-03 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/click_online/9504208.stm | accessdate = 2011-07-02 | archive-date = 2011-06-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110606113827/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/click_online/9504208.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.electronicsweekly.com/Articles/2011/05/25/51129/Dongle-computer-lets-kids-discover-programming-on-a.htm | title = Dongle computer lets kids discover programming on a TV | accessdate = 2011-07-11 | last = Bush | first = Steve | date = 2011-05-25 | publisher = [[Electronics_Weekly|Electronics Weekly]] | archive-date = 2011-11-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111122110522/http://www.electronicsweekly.com/Articles/2011/05/25/51129/Dongle-computer-lets-kids-discover-programming-on-a.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

树莓派系列计算机每一代均使用[[博通|博通]]（Broadcom）出產的[[ARM架構|ARM架構]]處理器，如今生产的机型（树莓派4B）[[内存|内存]]在2GB和8GB之間，主要[[TF卡|TF卡]]作爲系统存儲媒体（初代使用[[SD卡|SD]]卡），配備[[USB|USB]]接口和[[HDMI|HDMI]]的視頻輸出（支持聲音輸出），内置[[Ethernet|Ethernet]]/[[WLAN|WLAN]]/[[Bluetooth|Bluetooth]]網絡鏈接的方式（依據型號決定），并且可使用多種操作系統。產品線型號分爲A型、B型、Zero型和ComputeModule計算卡。

[[Raspberry_Pi_OS|Raspberry Pi OS]]是官方推出的操作系统，适用于所有型号的树莓派，树莓派基金会网站也提供了[[Ubuntu_MATE|Ubuntu MATE]]、Ubuntu Core、Ubuntu Server、OSMC等第三方系统供大众下载。<ref name="raspberrypi_os">{{Cite web|title=Raspberry Pi Downloads - Software for the Raspberry Pi|url=https://www.raspberrypi.org/downloads/|accessdate=2020-04-25|work=Raspberry Pi|language=|archive-date=2020-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326022417/https://www.raspberrypi.org/downloads/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

