pi.org/archives/1588 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。9月5日树莓派基金会公布了B型第二次修订版<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.raspberrypi.org/archives/1929 |title= Upcoming board revision |publisher= Raspberrypi.org |date= 2012-09-06 |accessdate= 2012-09-05 |archive-date= 2014-03-31 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140331044851/http://www.raspberrypi.org/archives/1929 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

